        public static Integer getResourceTypeId​(String resourceType)
        Retrieves the id for the name contained in the passed resource type, for the current tenant-datastore. If not found, null is returned.
        Parameters:
        resourceType - A valid FHIR search parameter name.
        Returns:
        Integer The id corresponding to the parameter name.
